data.description: Come check out the opportunity to build instant equity. An investment that promises both value and location advantages.  This ranch-style home with great curb appeal & front covered porch is set within a sought-after neighborhood, it is brimming with potential despite needing some interior cosmetic work. The 3BR, 1.5BA has an open concept kitchen, breakfast bar, dining room, living room and family room.  The sliding glass patio doors lead out to large backyard and covered patio.  Improvements include Concrete driveway, sidewalk and garage (13), Roof, Soffit, Fascia (06), Water heater (18), AC/Furnace (13). There have been similar sold comparables in the past year that have sold from $350k to $415K.
